  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $2000</p><p>Duration: immediate till 31 Jun 2026</p><p>Working Days & Hours: 8am to 5pm / 830am to 530pm (Mon to Fri)</p><p>8am to 12pm / 830am to 1230m (Every sat)</p><p>Location: Tampines North</p><p></p><p>•  Performs picking/packing of medications under Bin Coding System</p><p>•  Supports Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX/EZYBOX Services for remote collection of medications</p><p>•  Assists in patient management of Scriptless Dispensing workflow</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in  any course</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg </p><p></p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p>allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg<a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
